	<div class="col-xs-9 col-xs-offset-1">
		<p>If you want arrows on the left and right sides you just need to add a 
		little bit of code as the last thing in the 'carousel slide' div. It will 
		be two anchor with href set to the id of the carousel with a # sign before. 
		One will have the class of 'left carousel-control' and data-slide='prev' 
		and the other will have the class of 'right carousel-control' and 
		data-slide='prev'. Inside each anchor tag you can place a a span with a 
		glyphicon.</p>
